### the-coach — smoke request catalog
### Run the system first:  aspire run --project src/TheCoach.AppHost
### Then send these against the API resource. The base URL is printed by the
### Aspire dashboard; override @host below to match (the dev HTTPS port varies).
###
### Auth: endpoints other than /health and the Stripe webhook require a Bearer
### token. Supply a TEST OIDC token via env — never inline a real one.

@host = https://localhost:7443
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### Liveness — anonymous, always on. Proves the app booted and the DB is reachable.
GET {{host}}/health

### OpenAPI document (development only).
GET {{host}}/openapi/v1.json

### Authorized endpoint without a token — MUST return 401 (security contract is on).
GET {{host}}/api/v1/automations

### Authorized endpoint with a test token — list automation workflows for the tenant.
GET {{host}}/api/v1/automations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Stripe webhook — anonymous by design (signature-verified, not bearer-authed).
POST {{host}}/api/v1/billing/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{ "type": "ping" }
